  <%- include ('./partials/header.ejs',currentUser) %>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <h2>What we're about !!!</h2>
      <p>
        R.I.O.T&copy; is an meetup group for marathon sprinters. These
        meetups help beginners to meet with experienced sprinters to kick
        start their sprinting journey, also helps experienced sprinters to
        discuss preparation strategies and have a great time!.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <h2>Why should you join?</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>
            Meet different sprinters who are preparing for or who have taken
            an interest in long distance races! Accumulate to share tips,
            discover preparing accomplices, and have a great time!.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            Have you at any point needed to do a 5K, Half Marathon or other
            marathon occasion? Well now's your opportunity to make your
            objective a reality. Start with our 10km long distance race
            meetup occasion and get tips from experienced sprinters.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            Are you an experienced sprinters ???, join our charity marathon
            meetup group where you can find fellow sprinters who run for a
            social cause.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
